- convert all these bubbling "binds" into fewer "delegates"

- instead of using ownerDocument = something arbitrary for widgets,
consider using ownerDocument = this.element; I think that will be a more natural standard,
and it will automatically enable bubbling since this.element will be on the DOM
ref: http://api.jquery.com/triggerHandler/



Free / Hobbyist / Pro / Enterprise - pay levels?
Free = free, very limited
Hobbyist = free stuff + pay-as-you-go ($ per map?)
Pro = up to N sitemaps stored, multiple user accounts
Enterprise = many accounts, unlimited sitemaps, extra features